{"type":null,"faqId":14014,"title":"荣耀 X1 7.0 是否支持 WLAN 直连？怎么操作？","answer":"<p>\n  <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">支持。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">您可以参考如下步骤进行设置：</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>1.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在主屏幕上点击<a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.3.1.1.1\"></a><b>设置</b></span><span> &gt; <b>WLAN</b></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>2.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击或滑动</span> <b><span>WLAN</span></b><span> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">后的开关至</span> <a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.3.2.2.1\"></a><b><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44734\" width=\"22\" height=\"16\" alt=\"\" /></span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，开启</span><span> WLAN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>3.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击</span> <b><span>WLAN </span></b><b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">直连</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，同时在需要接受文件的设备上开启</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">直连。荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0&nbsp; </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">会自动搜索可连接的设备。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>4.<span style=\"font-size:7pt;line-height:normal;font-family:'Times New Roman';\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">点击需要共享的设备名称与之建立连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <a name=\"figd0e697\"></a><a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.4.1\"></a><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44735\" width=\"529\" height=\"422\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <span>&nbsp;</span>\n</p>\n<p>\n  <a name=\"gen-id1.3.4.2.5\"></a><span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=44736\" width=\"44\" height=\"11\" alt=\"\" /></span>\n</p>\n<blockquote style=\"margin:0 0 0 40px;border:none;padding:0px;\">\n  <p>\n    <span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">如果荣耀</span><span> X1 7.0 </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">与需要共享文件的设备已连接至同一</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">网络，且均已经开启</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">直连，则二者无需手动建立</span><span> WLAN </span><span style=\"font-family:楷体_GB2312;\">直连，可以直接共享文件。（其他厂商的设备不一定支持此策略，连接前请确认其他设备是否支持）。</span>\n  </p>\n</blockquote>","faqTypeId":170,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"5674","faqTypeCode":"Tablet-Internet-Data-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1406077795000,"seriesProductName":"7D-501u","visitedTimes":79,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"wifi直连,wifi共享,共享文件,发送文件、wifi direct","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}